author: David Ehrlich
title: ‘Landline’ Review: ‘Obvious Child’ Duo Gillian Robespierre And Jenny Slate Reunite For A Bigger, Better, Messier Comedy That’s Totally Off The Hook
text: An honestly told story about the messiness of human relationships, this period comedy represents a huge step forward for everyone involved.
